cut:-It is use to display data columm
wise.
Synatx:- cut -f '3' -d '|' student.


sort:- It is use do sorting (sort according to a sky and also sort the heading).
Synatx:- sort -k '2' -t '|' student .

Chmod:- It is use to change the mode of the file.
Syntax:- chmode 775 student.


sed command(stream lime editor):- used to display data row wise (can't print specific line).
Synatx:- sed -n '5p' hello.


Substitution:- It is use to do substitution.
Syntax:- sed 's/old value/new value/g' filename.


grep:- It is use to search any keyword from a file.
Synatx:- grep hello filename.
